00:26:10,612 --> 00:26:12,673
a person on my team who I think is brilliant

425
00:26:12,673 --> 00:26:13,994
and that I want to work with,

426
00:26:13,994 --> 00:26:17,236
but may not have those exact skill sets

427
00:26:17,236 --> 00:26:21,699
that I needed to get the game done as I was envisioning it.

428
00:26:21,699 --> 00:26:22,260
So that makes sense.

